                  "pageTitle": "Ulfrun's Endurance",
                  "pageId": 1580216,
                  "revisionId": 2729828,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Despite its description, the augment only restores a charge if the enemy directly targeted by the lunge attack dies instantly or due to the Slash procs from abilities such as Ulfrun's Descent or Fangs of Raksh while in range. This also applies to helminth abilities such as Aquablades , as long as the Slash proc is caused by an ability Voruna has cast. This includes inflicting a Slash proc with a weapon, then duplicating it with Sickening Pulse , since the duplicated procs are created by an ability. Slash procs made by ally abilities do not count for restoring charges."
                }
              },
              {
